{"tid":2259310,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「警世」 抽螞蟻就係幫對家!!!","createTime":"2020-10-26T17:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T08:10:09.000Z","uid":225437,"like":76,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"52310b0d668d1faa1e48a19940001d17925d035e","tid":2259310,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:07:45.000Z","msg":"螞蟻定左下個月5號上市<br />\n我見唔少巴打話要抽嚟賺錢<br />\n但大家知唔知道抽ipo推高招股價(直至上限價<br />\n係會令螞蟻集多左資 cap多左水<br />\n平時點買中概股都冇所謂<br />\n我自己都有買啲中概股<br />\n反正二手市場唔影響佢地既現金流<br />\n但一手市場抽ipo推高招股價就係幫黨企<br />\n令佢地cap多左水<br />\n如果真係好想買螞蟻股票既<br />\n可以等上左市或者暗盤買都唔成問題<br />\n而且偉大既麵神都燈過螞蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲打諗清楚係咪要送錢俾對家洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0cbaf588f2af22e7a05b1581f094489faa821c","tid":2259310,"uid":366655,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:09:08.000Z","msg":"抽螞蟻只是工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e8828e556e27cce2c19e7b89a64106616ef40d","tid":2259310,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b7f5f4b7f73db56a61f243f8262911d91b189bf","tid":2259310,"uid":225437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efbe189a102ecca6c70f927c1ae10e3a0fde63ef","tid":2259310,"uid":31765,"like":32,"dislike":6,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"你條仆街咪又係抽<br />\n咪擾敵啦<br />\n講錢就乜手足都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67028d2659b6910c659fc2c2d2ccabac3d685009","tid":2259310,"uid":362865,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:34:53.000Z","msg":"全文重點<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">而且偉大既麵神都燈過螞蟻</span></span>"},{"pid":"ca2cfc134ed2e8fc51ca4db25b393f7ef8a60d02","tid":2259310,"uid":370897,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedB